This study evaluates the clinical efficacy and study the therapeutic mechanism of a kind of traditional Chinese medicine colonic dialysis on Chronic kidney disease (CKD) 5 without blood dialysis therapy in adults.

 Half of participants will receive conventional integrated therapy on chronic renal failure (CRF), while the other half will receive integrated therapy on CRF and traditional Chinese medicine colonic dialysis.

